{"tid":2094341,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"世界最幸福國度-北歐極光之旅","createTime":"2020-07-04T14:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T11:38:55.000Z","uid":174716,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7210645f8856b90a6e1df6c0293f45c77d8d2a67","tid":2094341,"uid":174716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:22:09.000Z","msg":"想當初因為睇過呢到嘅巴絲遊記後，令我鼓起勇氣一個人去旅行。而事後一路以嚟都想打篇遊記紀錄番所見所聞，奈何怕文筆唔好怕吸引唔到人怕呢個時期比較敏感而一路都冇打到。<br />\n然而，我更怕嘅係有一日我會忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望會有人鍾意睇啦<br />\n以下係少少劣作 ps.人生第一次去旅行用相機影相，請高抬貴手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fs2eTG8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffs2eTG8.jpg&h=a32af2d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MEW3M2g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMEW3M2g.jpg&h=4b9942b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sxbjknn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsxbjknn.jpg&h=2d92a6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTOxFn8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTOxFn8.jpg&h=71b23dfa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9e2a6a14c3e827ae5994c824038902712667131","tid":2094341,"uid":174716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T14:32:24.000Z","msg":"旅程由芬蘭嘅Rovaniemi 講起，由於前一晚都冇特別plan第二日嘅行程，所以呢一日都訓到比較晏先check out，<br />\n之後就正式開始踏上去瑞典嘅旅途。<br />\n由Rovaniemi搭個零鐘火車去到Kemi後，我就要轉巴士去瑞典同芬蘭嘅邊境-Haparanda-Tornio。<br />\n<br />\n誇越一條小橋後，就正式踏入瑞典國土了，一落車就見到ikea<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2dcq0pZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2dcq0pZ.jpg&h=ed9a1921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於完全冇做功課，只好去旅客中心問人有咩方法去到北部Kiruna<br />\n但原來尾班巴士早已經喺13:40開出，最快嘅車要等到第二朝6:50。再check埋火車，第二朝5:16先有火車由Lulea 去Kiruna。到咗呢一刻其實都冇辦法，只好決定stay喺到定係去咗Lulea先。<br />\n咁呢個旅客中心嘅職員係一個婆婆黎，佢都好好人咁幫我查晒所有車班次，同埋呢到嘅住宿情況同價格，後來我呢個見步行步嘅人都係決定搭去Lulea再算。<br />\n咁由於我事前有買Eurail pass ，知道有架巴士係連接Haparanda同Lulea呢個冇火車鐵路覆蓋嘅路線，我就要搵架20號巴士嘅站，google咗要行廿幾分鐘。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/maeEkqH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmaeEkqH.jpg&h=9eb5178d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入到去發現完全唔似車站，見到一男一女坐喺到咁就問下啦。原來我所搵嘅站就係喺我一開始行黎嗰到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔記得係比google map老點定唔知隻眼發咩神經，咁都睇得錯<br />\n佢地都好好人咁問洗唔洗車我去個站呀，我就唔係幾好意思，話行去都唔算太遠，所以就拒絕咗佢地嘅好意。<br />\n而呢個就係我對瑞典嘅第一印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />先啱啱到步冇幾耐就遇到幾個咁好嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yyagnEK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyyagnEK.jpg&h=c922815d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過一過隔離，時區慢咗一個鐘，外面天已全黑<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d182e2c6a13cb576ff98b90d0983d1f3870c4ce","tid":2094341,"uid":270456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T16:46:21.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />期待樓豬更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cadf382a838fce599cbd14113506ba5a2c61d46a","tid":2094341,"uid":174716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:17:44.000Z","msg":"之後就順利搭到架巴士，接近兩個鐘嘅車程就黎到Lulea<br />\n落車後就先火車站睇睇，唔知係細站關係定點，先6點零就已經冇職員喺站內，然後又有班望落好似難民嘅人喺到好大聲咁傾計，此地不宜久留嘅情況下就選擇行咗出去街到。<br />\n街上人煙稀少，天氣亦有啲凍，我一路行一路check下附近嘅住宿，可能始終唔係旅遊區，選擇又少又貴，於是都冇打算喺到留一晚。自己完全唔知下一步應該點做嘅情況下，就唯有去番火車站呢個室內地方再作打算。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lcu84CD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLcu84CD.jpg&h=885be9be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到火車班次後就靈機一觸，自己一路都諗辦法上北部，但其實換個路線先去斯德哥爾摩都得喎，而且搭到過夜火車又慳番晚住宿錢之餘又唔會浪費時間。<br />\n於是我就決定咗等呢班火車，但有個問題就係就算有火車pass，搭過夜火車都需要事先留位，我就完全冇呢個經驗。喺站外見到個男人，我諗佢都係瑞典人黎，我就問佢可以點樣喺網上訂位？ 可惜佢都唔清楚，但佢都好好人咁想話幫我上網問人<br />\n<br />\n隨著愈黎愈接近火車開出時間，終於見到有工作人員出現了，見到個女職員後我就如實同佢講我有火車pass，但我冇辦法上網reserve位，佢都好好人肯通融我比我坐呢班火車，令我行程得以順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總覺得去旅行遇到好嘅人會對個地方大大加分，而我黎到瑞典短短幾個鐘內已經遇到幾個咁nice嘅人，令我更加期待黎緊嘅旅途。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rmsuPen.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrmsuPen.jpg&h=a140248f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fJksAUo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfJksAUo.jpg&h=d805a18e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n打個卡先，應該呢世都唔會再有機會踏足呢個城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7247b28125de76e3c4ef679b70f56120c29f6cf","tid":2094341,"uid":174716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d182e2c6a13cb576ff98b90d0983d1f3870c4ce","tid":2094341,"uid":270456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T16:46:21.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />期待樓豬更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:18:26.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會唔會有啲咩改善建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb28a16f9d2a4d05cc89f302e948e096b06931e","tid":2094341,"uid":270456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7247b28125de76e3c4ef679b70f56120c29f6cf","tid":2094341,"uid":174716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d182e2c6a13cb576ff98b90d0983d1f3870c4ce","tid":2094341,"uid":270456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T16:46:21.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />期待樓豬更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:18:26.000Z","msg":"多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會唔會有啲咩改善建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T10:19:35.000Z","msg":"樓豬加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"328900b5e81e7a5939835031bdbcb0000c85589e","tid":2094341,"uid":174716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T11:26:12.000Z","msg":"順利搭到呢班火車後就開始搵住宿，間hostel一百蚊有找<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />瑞典果然物價親民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由於係被通融嘅情況下搭到，呢一晚只可以坐住咁渡過。<br />\n<br />\n經過十二個半鐘嘅車程後終於黎到Stockholm ，我帶住疲倦嘅身軀先去hostel check in，好彩嘅係咁早就可以入住。去到hostel我梳洗完後就先去附近食一個幾乎每一篇瑞典遊記都會見到嘅魚湯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ohao139.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhao139.jpg&h=6cb7e132&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2maPXCU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2maPXCU.jpg&h=cd8a777e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n啖啖肉好足料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d1639e74598a173be24560fec4722f2047cbb5","tid":2094341,"uid":174716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T11:38:55.000Z","msg":"食完後都係喺附近慢慢行下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kfcbrzm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkfcbrzm.jpg&h=b3e63d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kcnrfs8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkcnrfs8.jpg&h=01b02147&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npHe8Ok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnpHe8Ok.jpg&h=486e5b76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w1ZATfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw1ZATfa.jpg&h=42be938c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ApE5v15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FApE5v15.jpg&h=cd318532&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e0MrZVz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe0MrZVz.jpg&h=c0d546ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r3vDQ2q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr3vDQ2q.jpg&h=7f019884&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}